node.text: I will accept whatever happens to me after I post this. I know it’s controversial. But I just needed a place to share without fear of getting cut off. Thank you guys for watching . 👊🏻👊🏻👊🏻

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Bobby Bones on August 10, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text:
Fun weekend in Arkansas with the Governor and his wife . Then Told some jokes . Here are a few of them …
—

It’s nice to marry a woman I know wouldn’t have talked to me in high school.  I’m not guessing… she literally wouldn’t.  Who can blame her?  She was 5. 
 

Governor Asa Hutchinson has 10k followers on Instagram but somehow isn’t verified. Its rough over there for the Governor. People are harsh. hes the only person I’ve ever seen get physical threats after posting a Bible verse!
